{"tid":1996063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯總理米舒斯京確診新冠肺炎　全國單日增7099宗創新高","createTime":"2020-04-30T17:15:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T17:58:46.000Z","uid":81228,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2de94e9d66923fc021e307d5b6ff9349c1254df5","tid":1996063,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T17:15:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://sputniknews.cn/images/103123/21/1031232124.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsputniknews.cn%2Fimages%2F103123%2F21%2F1031232124.jpg&h=b4592481&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯新冠肺炎疫情有惡化趨勢，當地疫情防控指揮部今日（30日）公布新增7099宗確診病例，再創單日新高。而總理米舒斯京向普京總統表示，自己已感染新冠病毒。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯新增7099宗確診病例，創單日新高，累計宗數達10.6萬。此外，再多101人死亡，死亡人數達1073人，新增1333人治愈，累計1.16萬宗。防控指揮部表示，新增患者中40%為無症狀感染者。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯成為全球第8個確診病例數破10萬的國家，其餘7個國家為美國、西班牙、意大利、法國、德國、英國和土耳其。<br />\n<br />\n總統普京早前宣布再度延長全國假期至5月11日，並要求各地繼續嚴格遵守當前所採取的疫情防控措施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1759708/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E7%B8%BD%E7%90%86%E7%B1%B3%E8%88%92%E6%96%AF%E4%BA%AC%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E5%96%AE%E6%97%A5%E5%A2%9E7099%E5%AE%97%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1759708%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%2590%2586%25E7%25B1%25B3%25E8%2588%2592%25E6%2596%25AF%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2596%25AE%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A2%259E7099%25E5%25AE%2597%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rMorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=d22afa9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1759708%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2